      <mxCell id="n_roster" parent="1" vertex="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;fillColor=#f0e6ff;strokeColor=#7b2d8b;" value="&lt;b&gt;Roster (Demo Layer) — POST /v1/roster&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; replays a DiscordChatExporter JSON export through the pipeline, 1 session / author&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; returns risk-ranked per-user table: band &amp;middot; confidence &amp;middot; posture &amp;middot; top cues &amp;middot; step-up / evasion flags&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; UI: Session | Roster tabs; file upload; bundled synthetic sample (4 demo personas)&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; &lt;b&gt;Consent boundary:&lt;/b&gt; own channel / consenting participants / synthetic data only"><mxGeometry x="430" y="880" width="700" height="120" as="geometry" /></mxCell></root>
